%h1 Listing users

%table
  %tr
    %th email
    %th fname
    %th lname
    %th username
    %th gender
    %th state
    %th zip
    %th country
    %th birthday
    %th
    %th
    %th

  - @users.each do |user|
    %tr
      %td= user.email
      %td= user.fname
      %td= user.lname
      %td= user.username
      %td= user.gender
      %td= user.state
      %td= user.zip
      %td= user.country
      %td= user.birthday
      %td= link_to 'Show', user
      %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_user_path(user)
      %td= link_to 'Destroy', user, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }

